@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ppctaz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v2 * (v1 + 0.82 * tmp + 0.09)) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.52 - v0 + 0.71)))
    v2 = 0.78
    tmp = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.59 * v2 + 0.49) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.49)))
    v2 = 0.01
    v2 = ((0.81 * (v1 + 0.17 / tmp + 0.79)) - wp.sin((v2 + 0.19 / tmp + 0.70)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.30)))
    v0 = 0.71
    data[tid] = v0
